&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They&amp;rsquo;re not derived from looking at the past&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There&amp;rsquo;s a phrase you&amp;rsquo;ll hear Brett and I use over and over again: &amp;ldquo;good explanations.&amp;rdquo; Good explanations are Deutsch&amp;rsquo;s improvement upon the scientific method.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Nullius in Verba</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/nullius-in-verba/</link><pubDate>Fri, 05 Mar 2021 18:19:15 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/nullius-in-verba/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/nullius-in-verba.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
